casebody.data:
Lamart CURRY, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
State of Florida DEPARTMENT OF REVENUE CHILD SUPPORT PROGRAM, et al., Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D18-1829 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. SEPTEMBER 26, 2018 ROTHENBERG, C.J., and SALTER and LINDSEY, JJ., concur.

Upon the Court's own motion, it is ordered that this administrative appeal from the Florida Department of Revenue, Child Support Program is dismissed for failure to comply with this Court's order dated September 7, 2018, and with the Florida Rules of Appellate Procedure.
